[~smarvin], [~scottb]: We need to capture the issue with the userdata field on the instance detail page as a KI for 4.0.  See Kyo's comment for the issue we need to document…

{code}
The userdata field is always showing an empty, disabled field whether the userdata actually contains data or not.
After an EBS instance is stopped, the userdata field will be enabled to allow the field to be edited. In such case, rather than editing, the userdata will be overwritten with the new data.
{code}
